WARC Input and Output Formats for Hadoop
========================================

[warc-hadoop](https://github.com/ept/warc-hadoop) is a Java library for working with
[WARC (Web Archive)](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_ARChive) files in Hadoop.

More information:

* [README](https://github.com/ept/warc-hadoop)

Created by [Martin Kleppmann](http://martin.kleppmann.com) (@[martinkl](https://twitter.com/martinkl)).
